name: docked-link
description: This jQuery plugin adds a fixed link below the fold anchored to either the center-left or center-right of your browser window. Simply specify the element/link, how far below the fold you'd like your link to appear (where the tripwire is), and which side of the browser window you'd like your link docked on.
author: Mike Petruniak <mike.petruniak@gmail.com>
